quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  56,39,Aliqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamandulo
  56,40,Neqela labantu (bezizukulwana) zamva
  56,41,Neqela lamadlelane angasekhohlo yintoni na amadlelane angasekhohlo
  56,42,"(Baya\tkuba)\tseMlilweni\totshisayo\tnamanzi\tashushu (kanobom)"
  56,43,Nethinzi lomsi omnyama thsuh
  56,44,Elingapholanga lingancedi nakunceda
  56,45,Inene bona kaloku bazanelisa ngobutyebi ngaphambili
  56,46,Kananjalo bona babethe gqolo ngokugabadela (ngezono ezikhulu)
  56,47,"Kwaye babesithi: “Xa sele sifile saba luthuli namathambo, siza kuphinda ngenene sivuswe"
  56,48,Nookhokho bethu nabo ngokunjalo?”
  56,49,"Yithi wena (Muhammad): “Inene abantu bokuqala nabantu bokugqibela"
  56,50,Baza kuqokelelelwa iMini ekhethiweyo.”
  56,51,Ke kaloku nina ndawonye nabo balahlekileyo baphikayo
  56,52,Niya kutyiswa umthi weZa’kkûm
  56,53,Nizalise izisu zenu ngawo
  56,54,Niphinde ngaphezu koko nisezwe amanzi atshisayo
  56,55,Kwaye niya kusela ukusela kweenkamela ezinxaniweyo
  56,56,Iya kuba bububele babo (abaza kubenzelwa) ngoMhla woVuko
  56,57,"Sinidalile nje, kungani na ukuba ningakholwa"
  56,58,Nikubonile phofu oko niye nikukhuphe
  56,59,Nini na abakudalayo nokuba siThi abanguMdali
  56,60,"Simisele ukufa phakathi kwenu, yaye Thina ngeKhe Soyiswe"
  56,61,Kangangokuba Siya kuyiguqula imbonakalo yenu Sinivelise ngenye imo eningayaziyo nina
  56,62,"Ke kaloku sele niyazi indalo yokuqala, aniyi kukhumbula ke"
  56,63,Niyibonile phofu (imbewu) leyo niyityalayo
  56,64,Nini na abayenza ikhule nokuba Sithi abakhulisi
  56,65,Ukuba beSinokuthanda beSingasuka Siyenze yome ibe bubutyobo nihlale nimangazekile
  56,66,"(Nithi): “Inene thina (ngoku) sisematyaleni"
  56,67,Thina sibandazelekile.”
  56,68,Niwabonile phofu amanzi lawo niwaselayo?”
  56,69,Nini na abaza nawo emafini nokuba SiThi abawathobayo
  56,70,"Ukuba beSithanda beSingasuka Siwenze akrakre, kungokuba kutheni ukuba ningabi nambulelo (kuAllâh)"
  56,71,Niwujongile phofu umlilo lowo niwulumekayo
  56,72,Nini na abavelisa umthi wawo nokuba SiThi abaVelisi (bawo)
  56,73,Siwenze wasisikhumbuzi (soMlilo wesiHogo) nembonelelo yabahambi
  56,74,Ngoko ke zukisa igama leNkosi yakho uMnini bukhulu